        E C U T I V E  P R O F I L E 

 
 
 



                                        
        C H A S E  P A R T
        N E R S



.






  
        SITE MENU


Mary
        Claire Chase,
        President, founded the firm in 2000 and brings over 20 years of
        experience in the recruitment of top executives working principally for
        Financial Services and Management Consulting firms, including Putnam
        Investments, Arthur D. Little, Inc., The Forum Corporation, Innovation
        Associates, Inc., and others.


Prior to launching
        Chase Partners, Ms. Chase served as Senior Vice President, Director of
        Executive Search for Putnam Investments, where she filled senior
        executive positions in all areas of the company, including investments,
        institutional and mutual fund sales and marketing, corporate
        development, finance, operations, systems, legal and human resources. 
        Ms. Chase also has held senior recruitment and human resources
        positions at Arthur D. Little, Inc., where she served as Director of
        Global Staffing and Development, leading the corporation�s recruitment
        and management development efforts;  The Forum Corporation, as Director
        of Human Resources; Lechmere, Inc., a division of Dayton Hudson
        Corporation, as Director of Executive Staffing and Development; and
        Jordan Marsh Company, as Human Resources Manager.
Ms.
        Chase graduated magna cum laude from Boston College. 

                             




